com.firebase.authwrapper.resultactivity.types.google

Class GoogleActivityInvoker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.firebase.authwrapper.resultactivity.common.ActivityInvoker
      • com.firebase.authwrapper.resultactivity.types.google.GoogleActivityInvoker

  • public class GoogleActivityInvoker
extends ActivityInvoker

    This class is the facebook implementation of class ActivityInvoker object. It contains method and properties relevant for authentication by using Google API.

    This singleton class is used for binding the FacebookProvider to FacebookResultActivity.
